In the INTEREST OF K.H. and K.H., Minor Children, J.H., Father, Appellant. No. 19-0203 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A father appeals the termination of his parental rights to his two children. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
